OL,3,CO'Toole says ministers have questions
OL,4,Cto answer over financial package
OL,6,FThe Leader of the Opposition and Chair
OL,7,Fof the Finance Committee, Matthew O'
OL,8,FToole, will seek further clarity on
OL,9,Fthe terms of the #3.3 billion pound
OL,10,Ffinancial package for restoring
OL,11,Fdevolution at the committee's first
OL,12,Fmeeting today.
OL,14,FIt comes after the UK Government told
OL,15,Fthe Executive that Stormont must raise
OL,16,Fat least #113 million pounds of
OL,17,Frevenue in the next budget in a letter
OL,18,Fto Finance Manager Caoimhe Archibald
OL,19,Fon Tuesday.
OL,21,FArchibald has said this.
