OL,3,CO'Toole says ministers have questions
OL,4,Cto answer over financial package
OL,6,FAfter days of "contradictory
OL,7,Fstatements and confusion", Mr O'Toole
OL,8,Fsaid he will call on Executive
OL,9,FMinisters and the Secretary of State
OL,10,Fto spell out the terms of the funding
OL,11,Fdeal and what it means for ordinary
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FThe South Belfast MLA said:
OL,16,F"There are still more questions than
OL,17,Fanswers over what exactly was agreed
OL,18,Fin the financial package between the
OL,19,FExecutive parties and the UK
OL,20,Fgovernment.
