OL,3,CO'Toole says ministers have questions
OL,4,Cto answer over financial package
OL,6,F"Despite time and space to nail down
OL,7,Fthe details there appear to be
OL,8,Ffundamental disagreements over what
OL,9,Fexactly has been agreed and the
OL,10,Fstrings attached.
OL,12,F"If the British government is
OL,13,Funilaterally imposing new charges on
OL,14,Fthe people of the north to pay for
OL,15,Fpolitical failure that would be
OL,16,Fprofoundly unacceptable, but the
OL,17,FExecutive parties should know not to
OL,18,Ftrust the Tories. All this should have
OL,19,Fbeen clarified before now.
