OL,3,CO'Toole says ministers have questions
OL,4,Cto answer over financial package
OL,6,F"This isn't just a political he-said-
OL,7,Fshe-said, this is about delivering
OL,8,Fbasic public services for the people
OL,9,Fof Northern Ireland and what they'll
OL,10,Fhave to pay for them. The UK
OL,11,Fgovernment has acknowledged that they
OL,12,Fhave been underfunding this place for
OL,13,Fyears so that too needs to be
OL,14,Frectified.
OL,16,F"I will be seeking further clarity on
OL,17,Fthis, starting with the first meeting
OL,18,Fof the new Finance Committee."
