OL,3,CO'Toole says ministers have questions
OL,4,Cto answer over financial package
OL,6,FThe UK government has always
OL,7,Fmaintained that the package is a "fair
OL,8,Fand generous offer".
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Chris
OL,11,FHeaton-Harris welcomed confirmation of
OL,12,Fthe settlement's details.
OL,14,F"This package tackles the immediate
OL,15,Fbudget pressures facing the restored
OL,16,Fexecutive and allows it to take action
OL,17,Fto rapidly stabilise public services,
OL,18,Fwhile increasing opportunities for
OL,19,Finvestment and improved
OL,20,Finfrastructure," he said.
